<p><strong><a href="https://feeds.feedblitz.com/~/t/0/0/finovate/~https://www.stylopay.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Stylopay</a></strong>&#8216;s <em>Zoqq </em>is a self-service application and management portal for corporate card programs. Apply in 30 minutes and get approved in 7 days. Pay only card cost.</p>
<p><strong>Features</strong></p>
<ul><li>Apply in 30 minutes and get approved in 7 days </li><li>Get and manage programs in different countries and different currencies</li><li>Start with 100 cards at low costs with complementary admin and user portals</li></ul>
<p><strong>Why it&#8217;s great</strong>
<br>Faster application, multi-currency card program, global reach!</p>
