					<description><![CDATA[<p>Research shows brands that excel in customer engagement often exceed their revenue goals. But how well is the financial services industry really responding to customers, and delivering on promises of “customer-centricity?”</p>
<p>The post <a rel="NOFOLLOW" rel="nofollow" href="https://feeds.feedblitz.com/~/647038150/0/finovate~Customer-Engagement-Tactics-to-Boost-Loyalty-and-Monetization/">Customer Engagement Tactics to Boost Loyalty and Monetization</a> appeared first on <a rel="NOFOLLOW" rel="nofollow" href="https://finovate.com">Finovate</a>.</p>
<div style="clear:both;padding-top:0.2em;"><a title="Like on Facebook" href="https://feeds.feedblitz.com/_/28/647038150/finovate"><img height="20" src="https://assets.feedblitz.com/i/fblike20.png" style="border:0;margin:0;padding:0;"></a>&#160;<a title="Pin it!" href="https://feeds.feedblitz.com/_/29/647038150/finovate,https%3a%2f%2ffinovate.com%2fwp-content%2fuploads%2f2021%2f03%2fCustomer-experience-1024x446.png"><img height="20" src="https://assets.feedblitz.com/i/pinterest20.png" style="border:0;margin:0;padding:0;"></a>&#160;<a title="Tweet This" href="https://feeds.feedblitz.com/_/24/647038150/finovate"><img height="20" src="https://assets.feedblitz.com/i/twitter20.png" style="border:0;margin:0;padding:0;"></a>&#160;<a title="Subscribe by email" href="https://feeds.feedblitz.com/_/19/647038150/finovate"><img height="20" src="https://assets.feedblitz.com/i/email20.png" style="border:0;margin:0;padding:0;"></a>&#160;<a title="Subscribe by RSS" href="https://feeds.feedblitz.com/_/20/647038150/finovate"><img height="20" src="https://assets.feedblitz.com/i/rss20.png" style="border:0;margin:0;padding:0;"></a>&nbsp;&#160;</div>]]>
